the Philippines
would have me.

07:03.990 --> 07:09.863 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The World
Jewish Congress,
the government of Germany, and
others condemned

07:09.963 --> 07:11.431 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
