couples planning
pregnancy.

07:32.952 --> 07:37.157 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Centers for Disease Control
and Prevention
now say men who've been exposed
to the virus

07:37.257 --> 07:39.793 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
