adversaries.

09:13.319 --> 09:17.757 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Palestinian President Mahmoud
Abbas shook
hands with Israeli Prime
Minister Benjamin

09:17.857 --> 09:24.330 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
