saw in mine
that the determination emanates
from deep

09:49.222 --> 09:53.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
self-persuasion and devotion to
the cause,
securing the country's future.

09:53.326 --> 09:57.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Netanyahu has
taken a hard
line on dealing with the
Palestinians, while

09:57.530 --> 10:01.568 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
