in English,
hailed the Nobel Peace Prize
winner as a visionary.

10:06.072 --> 10:09.142 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BENJAMIN NETANYAHU: Shimon lived
a life of
purpose.

10:09.242 --> 10:12.946 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
