William Brangham.

12:30.617 --> 12:42.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: For high
school seniors
around the country and their
families, it's

12:42.895 --> 12:46.299 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
