college applications
and costs.

12:46.399 --> 12:50.570 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A key to all of it, of course,
is, what kind
of financial aid can they
receive?

12:50.670 --> 12:55.074 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
