12:57.810 --> 13:01.848 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Starting this weekend, there are
important
changes for a student filling
out the Free

13:01.948 --> 13:04.984 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Application for Federal Student
Aid, also
known as FAFSA.

13:05.084 --> 13:08.688 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For one thing, they will be able
to fill it
out months earlier, in the hopes
of getting

13:08.788 --> 13:11.324 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
