13:13.259 --> 13:15.962 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Kim Cook is the executive
director of the
National College Access Network,
which works

13:16.062 --> 13:17.497 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
