significance of what's
happening this weekend?

13:19.766 --> 13:21.668 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KIM COOK, Executive Director,
National College
Access Network: It's tremendous.

13:21.768 --> 13:28.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right now, over 1.4 million
students left
$2.7 billion in financial aid on
the table

13:28.307 --> 13:31.511 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
