the form
earlier and easier for students
are significant

13:36.849 --> 13:41.220 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
in helping many of those
low-income students
access the money they need to
attend college.

13:41.320 --> 13:44.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And one of the
significant
complaints was how complex it
was, how much

13:44.724 --> 13:46.492 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
