13:46.592 --> 13:49.128 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Now apparently there is a
connection between
your previous tax filing that
you can sort

13:49.228 --> 13:51.164 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of autopopulate online.

13:51.264 --> 13:56.469 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KIM COOK: There is, so that's
called the Internal
Revenue Service data retrieval
tool in lingo.

13:56.569 --> 14:01.074 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What's significant about these
changes that
are coming online tomorrow are
that more students

14:01.174 --> 14:06.846 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
