college choice.

14:46.786 --> 14:51.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
More importantly, on the front
end, there
was a crunch that we asked
students to think

14:51.124 --> 14:56.429 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about which colleges they would
apply or go
to before they had any sense of
their aid

14:56.529 --> 15:01.067 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
eligibility, never mind what
they will have
now, which is a commitment of
federal student

15:01.167 --> 15:05.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
aid on the front end, as early
as October
now, as they go into their
college search

15:05.505 --> 15:07.306 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and application time.

15:07.406 --> 15:10.476 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, this was
part of the
general disincentive over kind
of the burdens

15:10.576 --> 15:13.479 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
