the other.

15:17.083 --> 15:17.984 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
KIM COOK: Right.

15:18.084 --> 15:19.952 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Right.

15:20.052 --> 15:24.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
