of a commitment

15:31.430 --> 15:35.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as they look around and, A, make
the important
decision that college is
affordable and something

15:35.768 --> 15:41.007 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for me, and, B, where to go,
that I have a
commitment of money in my pocket
to make this

15:41.107 --> 15:42.742 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
possible.

15:42.842 --> 15:44.844 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, what
