information earlier,
but they can't be pressured to
commit to an

16:19.178 --> 16:21.047 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
aid package before May 1.

16:21.147 --> 16:24.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now, you said
in the beginning,
but it's kind of staggering to
think about

16:24.116 --> 16:25.418 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
