about America
through our movies.

48:34.545 --> 48:39.717 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I will go to Syria and I
will watch their
movies and talk to their
filmmakers and see

48:39.817 --> 48:41.819 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
