culture.

48:41.919 --> 48:44.722 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And physical abuse was a common
element.

48:44.822 --> 48:50.861 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Everybody I met had been beaten,
by their
parents, or their schoolteachers
or the police.

48:50.961 --> 48:57.735 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, it was a culture that
had already
suffered an enormous amount of
trauma.

48:57.835 --> 49:01.672 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And you know, my fixer, this
lovely young
woman, her...

49:01.772 --> 49:04.208 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Fixer is the
local producer
there.

49:04.308 --> 49:06.110 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LAWRENCE WRIGHT: Yes.

49:06.210 --> 49:09.880 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
