49:25.229 --> 49:34.772 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think a lot of times, when
America wanders
into regions that it so poorly
understands,

49:34.872 --> 49:37.608 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
