49:37.708 --> 49:45.149 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Iraq was a classic example of us
becoming
involved in a culture that we
totally didn't

49:45.249 --> 49:46.984 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
