49:55.926 --> 49:58.896 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Did it, when you look back now?

49:58.996 --> 50:02.099 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LAWRENCE WRIGHT: America's
changed profoundly.

50:02.199 --> 50:08.873 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
